{"tid":2220792,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"BNO持有人申請提走MPF被拒 受託人指明年才生效 回鄉證移居中國則迅速獲批","createTime":"2020-09-28T02:09:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-28T11:35:47.000Z","uid":48083,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e7df5b17c6752be68d6b51eab790e7ba98b01327","tid":2220792,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T02:09:55.000Z","msg":"....本報向五大受託人查詢提走MPF的申請流程，但原來目前只持BNO並未合資格申請，要待明年1月新BNO簽證生效後再審批。不過，有持回鄉證申請人改為長居內地，宣誓後已順利獲批。<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n陳先生（化名）早前以BNO申請提早領取MPF同告失敗。他表示，自己已去民政署宣誓永久離開香港到英國，但並未通過其MPF受託人東亞銀行審批。「我話會同太太去美國探仔，再去英國用BNO生活，但銀行就話BNO唔等於係移民離港，唔可以提早攞MPF走。」不過，由於陳先生本身亦定居於內地，而回鄉證屬於獲准在國內居住的證件，故陳先生期後再重新宣誓永久離開香港到中國居住，便成功通過東亞審批。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200928/AEPOWS2X5FEURN6LWUBWV23BOY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200928%2FAEPOWS2X5FEURN6LWUBWV23BOY%2F&d=4SaXJ4tauImRU00LhBBHUr9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=356747ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200928%2FAEPOWS2X5FEURN6LWUBWV23BOY%2F&h=00273d18\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200928/AEPOWS2X5FEURN6LWUBWV23BOY/</a>"},{"pid":"46519c6f9444e6d4158cfce9a1b8c793057066b0","tid":2220792,"uid":43785,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T02:16:47.000Z","msg":"好正常姐下話，你話走都要睇你點走。<br />\n依家都未開始，唔批就唔批架啦。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一生人拿一次，人地唔會難為你掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"107907c5c055635222a46206761f581716e4ba31","tid":2220792,"uid":68689,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T02:22:48.000Z","msg":"香港係中國既 點解話住果到係離開香港 又係死港獨撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b7ff5d73b6f7fc6d2beb001b7e7a1dfe3d8305c","tid":2220792,"uid":273703,"like":0,"di